a20641ea-be72-4c76-9051-84016483c8f9-0
00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.767
The Internet and social media
latforms allow us to connect

a20641ea-be72-4c76-9051-84016483c8f9-1
00:00:03.767 --> 00:00:07.000
with our friends, family, and
peers in a variety of ways.

b6239987-b813-4739-a1f4-a69998bb59a7-0
00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:10.372
It's a great way to keep in
touch, but sometimes people take

b6239987-b813-4739-a1f4-a69998bb59a7-1
00:00:10.372 --> 00:00:13.185
advantage of these platform's
and use them to sread negative

b6239987-b813-4739-a1f4-a69998bb59a7-2
00:00:13.185 --> 00:00:14.200
messages about others.

20ebaf3d-8c1c-4679-9da0-98b27a387b44-0
00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:18.483
Cyberbullying or bullying that
takes place on the Internet can

20ebaf3d-8c1c-4679-9da0-98b27a387b44-1
00:00:18.483 --> 00:00:20.560
be just as bad as bullying in
person.

c171a552-f272-4e2e-aa6e-e647aba13ae6-0
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.913
People can use the Internet to
send hurtful messages to

c171a552-f272-4e2e-aa6e-e647aba13ae6-1
00:00:23.913 --> 00:00:26.578
someone, sread fake rumors, or
share someone's private

c171a552-f272-4e2e-aa6e-e647aba13ae6-2
00:00:26.578 --> 00:00:28.079
information without permission.

dc274f41-4afb-474d-8938-b6721afe4e73-0
00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:31.764
The results of cyberbullying can
be just as impacting as

dc274f41-4afb-474d-8938-b6721afe4e73-1
00:00:31.764 --> 00:00:32.710
Facetoface bullying.

e7da8030-0f06-465a-ad6e-bad96dab3405-0
00:00:33.630 --> 00:00:36.699
When someone is cyberbullied,
their feelings can be hurt and

e7da8030-0f06-465a-ad6e-bad96dab3405-1
00:00:36.699 --> 00:00:38.310
their reputation can be damaged.

cf03a05b-36e7-4f17-8c9b-e778989e3000-0
00:00:39.030 --> 00:00:41.637
You can't always revent
cyberbullying, but you can play

cf03a05b-36e7-4f17-8c9b-e778989e3000-1
00:00:41.637 --> 00:00:44.570
a part in making the Internet a
friendlier and safer place for

cf03a05b-36e7-4f17-8c9b-e778989e3000-2
00:00:44.570 --> 00:00:44.990
everyone.

4e2217ce-7921-4f66-94cf-a4f9a0edc358-0
00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:48.775
Here are some guidelines you can
follow to promote civility

4e2217ce-7921-4f66-94cf-a4f9a0edc358-1
00:00:48.775 --> 00:00:49.110
online.

b4f5562b-5993-4d11-845b-c3a7658be15d-0
00:00:49.990 --> 00:00:52.372
First simly avoid sending
negative messages an

b4f5562b-5993-4d11-845b-c3a7658be15d-1
00:00:52.372 --> 00:00:55.110
participating in behavior that
can hurt someone else.

7906366a-f1b0-46ae-be98-274e6ff499a8-0
00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:56.910
Resect differences.

0cec8528-2940-4f57-8dd4-6d496ebc0847-0
00:00:57.260 --> 00:00:59.672
When you interact with people
online, respect their

0cec8528-2940-4f57-8dd4-6d496ebc0847-1
00:00:59.672 --> 00:01:00.740
differences in opinion.

e6d2fdad-2b34-483d-9b9d-4cde7f57f8e2-0
00:01:00.740 --> 00:01:02.180
Experience an culture.

5b9caf76-5bc7-4673-a089-3de102978267-0
00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:05.449
Even if you don't agree with
something that another person

5b9caf76-5bc7-4673-a089-3de102978267-1
00:01:05.449 --> 00:01:08.257
shares online, you should still
treat them with respect and make

5b9caf76-5bc7-4673-a089-3de102978267-2
00:01:08.257 --> 00:01:10.504
the Internet a friendly place
for communication and

5b9caf76-5bc7-4673-a089-3de102978267-3
00:01:10.504 --> 00:01:10.979
discussion.

a2bde1ce-52b8-4393-ae86-f8ed74caad7d-0
00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:15.302
Think about the consequences of
sharing before you share or post

a2bde1ce-52b8-4393-ae86-f8ed74caad7d-1
00:01:15.302 --> 00:01:16.140
anything online.

0dbe3164-f919-4a0e-9aaa-a46a358fbe9a-0
00:01:16.340 --> 00:01:19.060
Always pause an think about the
consequences of doing so.

3f2914ca-7b7b-40de-9af6-41da9eb8747e-0
00:01:19.780 --> 00:01:21.260
Will your message hurt someone
else?

846d8a38-9746-4166-aaee-bf1aea11db0a-0
00:01:21.700 --> 00:01:24.755
Will it damage your reputation
or the safety or reputation of

846d8a38-9746-4166-aaee-bf1aea11db0a-1
00:01:24.755 --> 00:01:25.100
others?

008d3a2d-bb6a-4c71-8239-1d0317b7a69b-0
00:01:25.990 --> 00:01:27.878
Does it contribute anything
constructive to the

008d3a2d-bb6a-4c71-8239-1d0317b7a69b-1
00:01:27.878 --> 00:01:28.390
conversation?

c8a57cb8-f7d0-4808-aec9-e5f35d4547bb-0
00:01:29.310 --> 00:01:31.966
If you feel unsafe online, you
should feel comfortable to

c8a57cb8-f7d0-4808-aec9-e5f35d4547bb-1
00:01:31.966 --> 00:01:34.715
remove yourself from a situation
an reort it to someone you

c8a57cb8-f7d0-4808-aec9-e5f35d4547bb-2
00:01:34.715 --> 00:01:34.990
trust.

5f4c1499-53b0-45c6-8c8f-20d02c5d7d51-0
00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:38.609
There is no rule requiring you
to engage in conversations or

5f4c1499-53b0-45c6-8c8f-20d02c5d7d51-1
00:01:38.609 --> 00:01:39.950
arguments with people online.

86cd67e0-57c5-41f6-aa3c-291de8c6e911-0
00:01:40.910 --> 00:01:43.912
And when you do see cruel or
dangerous activity online, offer

86cd67e0-57c5-41f6-aa3c-291de8c6e911-1
00:01:43.912 --> 00:01:46.865
to support those involved and
report the incident to someone

86cd67e0-57c5-41f6-aa3c-291de8c6e911-2
00:01:46.865 --> 00:01:47.350
you trust.

796fff28-20ab-4052-acb0-d3764a6db5bc-0
00:01:48.470 --> 00:01:51.442
We can all lay a part in being
responsible digital citizens

796fff28-20ab-4052-acb0-d3764a6db5bc-1
00:01:51.442 --> 00:01:54.464
online and making the Internet a
safe and friendly place for

796fff28-20ab-4052-acb0-d3764a6db5bc-2
00:01:54.464 --> 00:01:54.910
everyone.